sentences: Ta on saanud märksa palju eelmisel aastal.
Ma olin saanud selle raamatu nädala lõpus.
Riik on saanud uue presidendi valimisedel.
context: 'Saanud' is the past participle of 'saada', meaning to receive or obtain something. It's commonly used in describing actions that have been completed and has a direct object.
